tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE influencer_partnerships (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  influencer_name TEXT,
  company_name TEXT,
  campaign_name TEXT,
  campaign_type TEXT,
  start_date DATE,
  end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(255),
    campaign_type VARCHAR(50),
    start_date DATE,
    end_date DATE
);
CREATE TABLE influencer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(50), email VARCHAR(50), followers INT);
CREATE TABLE partnership (id INT PRIMARY KEY, influencer_id INT, brand_name VARCHAR(50), contract_start_date DATE, contract_end_date DATE);
CREATE TABLE campaign (id INT PRIMARY KEY, partnership_id INT, campaign_name VARCHAR(50), campaign_start_date DATE, campaign_end_date DATE);

CREATE TABLE influencer (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name STRING, followers INT); CREATE TABLE campaign (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name STRING, start_date DATE, end_date DATE); CREATE TABLE partnership (id INT PRIMARY KEY, influencer_id INT, campaign_id INT, payment DECIMAL); CREATE TABLE collaboration (id INT PRIMARY KEY, campaign_id INT, influencer_id INT, engagement_rate FLOAT);

CREATE TABLE influencers (
    influencer_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_name VARCHAR(255),
    influencer_email VARCHAR(255),
    followers_count INT
)

CREATE TABLE campaigns (
    campaign_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    campaign_name VARCHAR(255),
    campaign_start_date DATE,
    campaign_end_date DATE
)

CREATE TABLE partnerships (
    partnership_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    campaign_id INT,
    partnership_type VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE collaboration_requests (
    request_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    campaign_id INT,
    request_status VARCHAR(255)
)

CREATE TABLE collaboration_history (
    history_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    influencer_id INT,
    campaign_id INT,
    collaboration_date DATE,
    engagement_level VARCHAR(255)
)
